name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. John LYNCH, Petitioner

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. John LYNCH, Petitioner.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 15th day of July, 2009, the “Verified Application for Permission to File Petition for Allowance of Appeal Nunc Pro Tunc ” is GRANTED. Counsel is directed to file a Petition for Allowance of Appeal within 15 days of this order.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. John LYNCH, Petitioner.

July 15, 2009.
